Node.Notes: Reuben, Simeon, Levi, Judah, Issachar, and Zebulun were all sons of Jacob's first wife Leah.
Joseph and Benjamin were sons of Rachel, Jacob's second wife, but Joseph is not listed because he was already in Egypt.
Dan and Naphtali were sons of Rachel's maid.
Gad and Asher were sons of Leah's maid.
Uncertain. Tree assumes all their service in which they made them serve [was] with rigor. Also possible in apposition to the two objects of the two preceding pp’s.
